HEADWORD: Abligurition
<hw>Ab*lig`u*ri"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>abligurito</ets>, fr. <ets>abligurire</ets> to spend in luxurious
